data.title: Office of History, National Institutes of Health
data.text:
PLEASE NOTE:

We are always adding images and updating records. If you do not see an image or information that you need, please contact the Office of NIH History and Stetten Museum or by telephone at 301.496.6610.

DISCLAIMER:

The images in this database do not contain specific alt-text due to proprietary software. However, the caption and the description in each image's Full Record provide a more complete description than a short alt-text can. For other accessibility issues, please see http://history.nih.gov/info/accessibility.html

Office of NIH History and Stetten Museum|Bldg 60| Suite 230|National Institutes of Health|Bethesda, MD 20814-1460 Phone: 301.496.6610|Email: history@nih.gov
